{
  "stem": "2004.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But by and large, as I mentioned before, the Polish Gentiles did not get along with the Czech Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the Poles claimed that the Czech part of Cieszyn was really a Polish-- was part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It should have never been given to the Czechs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And therefore, if you remember history, in 1938 when the Nazis marched into Czechoslovakia, which was-- oh, it was before they actually went, when Czechoslovakia was divided, which was the famous Chamberlain agreement.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Poland, the Polish government, took possession of the Czech part of Cieszyn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was not only the Czech part of Cieszyn, but it was also the surrounding area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So for a while-- for approximately a little over a year, there was no more Czech.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was all Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It all belonged to Poland then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was annexed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was annexed by Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't affect us in any way because we were free to go before to the Czech side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only time-- the only difference was that we no longer needed the passport to cross over to the other side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Other than that, it really didn't affect us in any way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We sort of felt sorry for the Czech population because we always found the Czech people-- and I'm referring to Gentile Czech people-- they were much more tolerant of their Jewish population than was the Polish Gentile population.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were more understanding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were-- they were easier to get along with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- well, that by itself was not threatening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what we-- my understanding-- and my understanding was primarily from what I heard from grown-ups-- was that the Poles, the Polish government, has contributed to the downfall of Czechoslovakia because the Germans grabbed the Sudetenland.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
